text: The County Ground is a football stadium located in Swindon, Wiltshire, England, and has been home to Swindon Town Football Club since 1896. It has an all-seated capacity of 15,728 currently, which has been the same level since the mid-1990s. Capacity: 15,729 Owner: Swindon Town F.C. Opened: 1862 Team: Swindon Town F.C.
